overview.en: ASSWAP aims to lower the ecological threshold for users to participate in DEFI, to create an integrated multi-chain ecological aggregation platform for five public chains, and to redefine a new standard for the anonymous cross-chain flow of crypto assets.
overview.zh: ASswap旨在降低用户参与Defi生态门槛，打造五大公链为一体多链生态聚合型平台，重新定义加密资产匿名跨链流动新标准。
